title: Robotech 20th Anniversary Soundtrack [mp3]
description:
This is the backgrundmusic, the themesongs, the main title and all the classic sounds from Robotech:

* The Macross Saga
* The Robotech Masters
* The New Generation

All the songs are from the English version, not the original japanese. (Tough the most tracks don&#039;t feature singing, but are just backgrund music)


They&#039;re all in pretty good quality.




Enjoy your listening!

/Schottis
